summary: A new architecture set for Skyrim
descriptionHtml:
Created by AlKoponen, converted by CFX.

Includes a test esp to demonstrate the new meshes, load it up and type "coc 00_PoorlordsKeep"

Thank you to AlKoponen on ShareCG for the meshes. The textures used are the vanilla Windhelm Stone, so it should be compatible with all texture mods.

Feel free to use this in your mods, just send me a link so I can see how you use them.
author: AlKoponen and CalledFireX
